# Most topics in this screen don't need an API key.
# If your chosen upstream (or your stack) does need one — e.g. a
# personal GitHub PAT for Topic 3 to lift the unauthenticated rate
# limit — keep it here, in .env, NEVER in source.
#
# Anything key-shaped detected in git history is an auto-fail (gitleaks).
#
# Example for Topic 3 (optional — unauthenticated 60 req/h works for the
# screen's traffic; PAT raises it to 5000 req/h):
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_replace-me
